Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@53051

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- #1916: Switch all the .po files to UTF-8
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 1.7.3
===========================================================
First release built by: madarche at: 2008-09-03T15:28:11
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/1.7.3
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@52925

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Set a more efficient configuration for tidy:
  -indent, -wrap 80, --hide-comments no
- #1890: Image without image breaks Image Gallery.
  Part of the fix includes setting 'is_required' to True by default for
  'preview' field in image layout (done in CPSDefault package).
  Another part of fix is to correctly handle 'is_required' field when no
  image was supplied to 'Image Widget'.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

===========================================================
