===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 1.7.0
===========================================================
First release built by: madarche at: 2008-01-15T12:19:24
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/1.7.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@52414

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- #1881: Provide an easy mean to resize the widget textareas.
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- #1864: CPSSubjectWidget breaks when a subject contains non-ascii characters.
- #1868: ZMI copy/paste of widgets is hazardous.
- In restricted code, replaced aq_base(obj) by obj.aq_inner.aq_explicit, since
  aq_base is not available in restricted code.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

