===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 1.6.0
===========================================================
First release built by: madarche at: 2007-10-19T12:21:16
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/1.6.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@52013

Requires
~~~~~~~~
- CPSI18n >= 1.0.0
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed #1844 : "It is impossible to import a vocabulary with items having
  accented characters in keys".
- Fixed #1850 : Empty keys get duplicated when displaying a vocabulary with
  Select Widgets.
- Made the MultiSelect Widget do case-insensitive sorting.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

