~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed #1819 : "Links in the Link Widget are HTML escaped".
- Fixed HTML validity of the URL Widget.
- Updated Spanish translation thanks to Jesús Martín.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

