===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 1.3.0
===========================================================
First release built by: gracinet at: 2007-02-06T14:46:06
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/1.3.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@50983

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- DataModel tells the StorageAdapters to write only those fields that
  have been modified or that the adapter didn't require;
  A new 'write_process_dependent_fields' property is used by some
  adapters to require those fields. This is backwards compatible.
===========================================================
