Package: CPSSchemas 1.2.0
===========================================================
First release built by: gracinet at: 2006-12-13T20:10:35
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/1.2.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@50571

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added a "size_min" option to the String Widget.
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixes #1795 : "cpsschemas_err_file_bad_suffix is not translated" by
  synchronizing the err and err_mapping translations with those of the .po
  files.
- Fixed i18n sorting in vocabularies.
- Fixed sorting in Select Widget and MultiSelect Widget when the translated
  option is on.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

