===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 0.56.0
===========================================================
First release built by: gracinet at: 2006-11-16T18:17:23
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/0.56.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@50008

Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Layout has 3 new properties (label, label_edit and is_i18n) that are passed as
  kw arguments to the layout_style to be able to label groups of widgets
- #1769: Select Widgets can add an empty key to vocabularies
- Added Zope External Editor sample configuration files for both Unix and
  Windows systems (featuring OpenOffice.org file formats).
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Added a maxlength attribute to conform to the rule
  "Fiche 1.4 : Pour chacune des images de la page, les textes dans l'attribut
  ALT font-ils moins de 60 caractères ?"
  cf. http://www.accessiweb.org/fr/guide_accessiweb/guide-accessiweb-fiche-1-4.html
- Applied the CPS style to the HTML editor window.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.55.5 [R1 build 2006/10/16-11:56 by madarche]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 49601
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Made it possible to call the unprepare method several times in the course of
  the validate method of a widget since it sometimes happens when validateError
  is called in the end in case of error.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

