===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 0.55.1
===========================================================
First release built by: ogrisel at: 2006-10-10T11:44:37
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/0.55.1
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@49442

Requires
~~~~~~~~
-
New features
~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed #1518 by adding a title field in the File Widget, Image Widget and Photo
  Widget. This title field is used as the "title" and "alt" attributes on
  HTML images declarations.
- Fixed #1380 : "open links in popups ?" by providing the openLinkInPopup
  JavaScript method to open links in popup in an accessible way and not
  breaking conformance to the XHTML 1.0 Strict DTD.
New internal features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- 

===========================================================
Package: CPSSchemas 0.55.0
===========================================================
First release built by: ben at: 2006-10-04T11:13:56
SVN Tag: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/tags/0.55.0
Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk@49290

Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Widgets have a new "readonly_if_expr" property.
- Added the possibility to have embedded HTML editor window in the Text Widget.
- Added an "xhtml_sanitize" property and functionality to the Text Widget.
- Added a "setUserModified" method on CPSVocabulary so that scripts triggered by
  user actions can prevent vocabularies from being overwritten.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Disk file field brought up to [32951] (aftermath of #1335)
- [OPTIM]: fixed abusive use of objectIds() in local voc lookup
- #1730: Calendar widget not working fine when language is Catalan
- Made it possible to create empty vocabularies through the use of
  the CPSInstaller verifyVocabularies method.
- Missing XML ZMI export tab on vocabularies
- Fixed wrong permission check on vocabularies_manage_form.pt.
- Fixed vocabularies_manage_form so that the buttons appear skinned + used
  better HTML markup.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Moved jscalendar lang/ subdir to calendar-lang/ to avoid name collisions.
- Moved BasicWidget.renderHtmlTag to CPSUtil.html
- Removed deprecated _isinstance use.

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.54.2 [R1 build 2006/08/07-16:38 by fermigier]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 48074
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- optional bypass of getEditableContent in datamodel commit (#1608 & #1714)

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.54.1 [R1 build 2006/08/03-09:20 by fermigier]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 47837
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- BBB hack for upgradability.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.54.0 [R1 build 2006/07/31-13:50 by fermigier]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 47588
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- CPSRevisionWidget to only display the revision of a proxy
- added auto_strip feature to the CPSLinesWidget
- #1702: Added new Catalan translation thanks to Santi Camps.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Generic MultiSelect Widget will validate if the selection is empty and the 
  widget is not required, or is required and accepting blank values;
- Allowed Select widgets to sort the entries (missing import)
- new widget: Email List Widget that combines Email and Lines widgets
- do not escape tag attributes as they are already xmlquoted by renderHtmlTag
- #1700: Epoz problems in Internet Explorer. This results in the total removal
  of Epoz support in CPS.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- All fields get a new method _getAllDependantFieldIds
- removed some zLOG deprecation warnings
- made the CPSEmailWidget able to support addresses of the form
  "Firstname Lastname <fl@fakeemail.com>"

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.53.0 [R1 build 2006/07/04-16:06 by gracinet]
** SVN URL: http://svn/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 46897
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- #1677: dependent fields didn't work for File Fields created by flexible
widgets (no preview, no indexing).
- Using LayoutTools renderLayout call with a context that has a 
  postCommitHook caused the hook to be called if the layout changed, which 
  on CPSDocuments would set the size to something wrong, and cause a commit
  transaction.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- All fields get a new method _getAllDependantFieldIds

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.52.0 [R1 build 2006/06/21-17:01 by gracinet]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 46686
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- The FCKEditor field now uses the same font shapes and color as the main
  content slot.
- GenericSelect and MultiGenericSelect widgets can use a
  MethodVocabularyWithContext vocabulary.
- Select Widget and other Generic Select widgets vocabularies can be sorted.
- made File and AttachedFile widgets more configurable: link to external editor,
  html preview and html printable preview are hideable thanks to properties
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Clicking to open the popup for photo widgets will not refresh anymore the
  document page
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added doc about HOWTO to use a server-side spellchecker with FCKeditor.
- renderHtmlTag uses std python library to escape attributes

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.51.0 [R1 build 2006/05/19-12:36 by fermigier]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 45740
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Schema handles what storage adapter to use.
- Added the "sorted" option to the CPSMultiSelectWidget.
- Add possibility not to commit the datamodel when rendering a layout via
  LayoutsTool.renderLayout.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Include document.css, default.css and custom.css in the css used for the
  editor area in FCKEditor.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.50.4 [R1 build 2006/05/02-16:50 by gracinet]
** SVN URL: http://svn/pub/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 45185
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Widgets and fields have their own export tab in ZMI
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- #1627: fixed hidden widgets inside compound widgets.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- "Generic Select widget" can be used with vocabulary that have integer keys

*******************************************
** CPSSchemas V0.50.3 [R1 build 2006/04/10-15:55 by gracinet]
** SVN URL: http://svn/pub/CPSSchemas/trunk Revision: 35055
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- #1542: lack of <table> element in XML file describing a layout
  doesn't erase the table anymore
- Updated brazilian portugese translations (thanks to mo.menezes@gmail.com).
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-

