~~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- renaming properties '*_str' and used '*_c' for computed attribute
  foo_expression_str -> foo_expr, foo_expression -> foo_expr_c
  foo_str -> foo, foo -> foo_c

